name: Launchpad: Non-POS Merchant Boarding
description:
The Launchpads Merchant Boarding API allows Worldpay partners to onboard merchants to Worldpay's Payments Platform. Please see the Getting Started page for more information.

To contact our certifications team, please email Certification2@fisglobal.com.
To contact the product team, please email APICustomerIntegration@fisglobal.com.

folders.name: Initiate Boarding Application
folders.description: Resources to create/edit and read pending boarding applications.

folders.name: Submit Application
folders.description: Resources to validate and submit the final application for boarding.

folders.name: Check Application Status
folders.description: Resource to check status of the application.

folders.name: Review and Sign Contract
folders.description: Resources to retrieve the contract and digitally sign.

folders.name: Check Launchpad health
folders.description: Resources to check the the health of Launchpad and its dependent down streams systems at regular intervals to check the system is up or down.
